

Clear Jam		SCHOOL:Transmutation	CLASSES:Ranger,Sorcerer,Wizard=1	COMPS:V, S		CASTTIME:1 swift action		RANGE:Touch	TARGETAREA:1 jammed firearm							DURATION:Instantaneous	SAVEINFO:None				SPELLRES:no			DESC:Any barrel jams in the target firearm are cleared. The firearm is loaded and ready to be fired. This spell has no effect on a weapon that is not jammed (see the jammed optional rule or the spell Rifle Jam).
Jam Barrel		SCHOOL:Conjuration	CLASSES:Ranger,Sorcerer,Wizard=1	COMPS:V, S		CASTTIME:1 standard action	RANGE:Touch	TARGETAREA:one firearm or one firearm carried by target creature	DURATION:Instantaneous	SAVEINFO:Will negates (object)	SPELLRES:Yes (object)	DESC:Your successful melee touch attack causes a jam in the targeted firearm. Clearing the jam takes one full-round action, and any ammunition in the firearm is lost.
Readied Pistol	SCHOOL:Conjuration	CLASSES:Ranger,Sorcerer,Wizard=2	COMPS:V, S, M	CASTTIME:1 standard action	RANGE:Touch	TARGETAREA:one firearm								DURATION:1 hour/level	SAVEINFO:None				SPELLRES:no			DESC:Target firearm is loaded and can be fired immediately. It may be fired five times without needing to be reloaded, and can be fired up to the attacker's full number of attacks each round as part of a full attack action (provided there are enough shots remaining). Additional castings of this spell do not stack, but they reset the number of shots left to 5. Material Component A single musket ball.
